Design
The program is designed to display the Indian national flag by drawing rectangular components over the frame. It then inserts the image of Ashoka Chakra in the middle.

Dependancies
1.Chakra.jpg(Used for displaying the Ashoka Chakra in the middle of the flag)

Usage
Compile the source code($javac IndianTricolour.java) and then run its class($java IndianTricolour).


     

